des: Say It Now is and advertising technology business on a mission to make it possible to engage with any advertising message using your voice. We call these actionable ads. This skill will guide you through how we work, what we offers latest news and reviews. You can learn more about what we do, who we are, our latest work and subscribe to news and offers. Just say Alexa, Open Say It Now!
